name: Peace Extreme Vespa
description:
Extreme Vespa was created by the Indonesian Vespa community, who are more into the exploration of Vespa to achieve a unique look and make it more standout. The flag is one of the chosen aspects they put on their "ekstriman".

With what happened in some countries and to capture this short period of what happens in our world, this extreme vespa spread the peace message to those people who will own it later.
